Package: CCMCR
Title: Multivariate Chi-Square and Robust Covariance Control Chart
    (CC-MCR)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Sergio Daniel", "Frutos Galarza", , "sergio_dan88@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Omar", "Ruiz Barzola", , "oruiz@espol.edu.ec", role = "aut"),
    person("Purificación", "Galindo Villardón", , "pgalindo@usal.es", role = "aut")
  )
Description: The CC-MCR is a multivariate control chart designed to
    monitor processes with multiple interrelated variables. Unlike
    traditional charts, this approach uses a QQ statistic based on the
    chi-square distribution and employs robust estimators to handle
    outliers and non-normal data.
